org.fujion.event

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fujion.event.Event
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChangeEvent, CloseEvent, DropEvent, ForwardedEvent, InputEvent, KeyEvent, LoadEvent, MouseEvent, OpenEvent, PropertychangeEvent, ResizeEvent, StatechangeEvent, TimerEvent

    public class Event
extends Object
    This is the base class for all events.

      • getRelatedTarget

        public BaseComponent getRelatedTarget()
        Returns the event's related target, if any. A related target is a secondary component that had some role in or relationship to the event. For example, for a mouseenter event, the target is the component entered; the related target is the component exited.
        Returns:
        The event's related target

      • getTargetId

        public String getTargetId()
        Returns the id of the DOM element that was the actual target of the event. This may be the same as the target's component id, but could also be a sub-element of the target.
        Returns:
        The target id.
